name: Fidget-Cube
descripcion: An unusually addicting, high-quality desk toy designed to help you focus. Fidget at work, in class and at home in style. Fidget Cube has six sides. Each side features something to fidget with: Click. Glide. Flip. Breathe. Roll. Spin.

name: Fidget-Spinners
descripcion: The Fidget Spinner is designed to relieve stress and anxiety. Helps you stay focused! This is a great toy for fidgeters. Flick and spin with just one or both hands. It is perfect for both adults and kids who love fidgeting.
